data.description: Welcome to this charming historic home located at 445 West Circle Avenue! This fixer-upper offers endless potential for those who appreciate the allure of restoring a piece of history. Boasting original woodwork and beautiful windows, this property exudes character and charm. Situated on over half an acre, the expansive yard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities and entertaining. Imagine hosting tailgate parties and then walking over to the field on Football Friday Nights! Don't miss out on this chance to own a piece of history in a great location. Whether you're an investor looking for a project or a homeowner with discerning taste, this property is waiting for you to unlock its true potential. Schedule a viewing today and let your imagination run wild!
